description.en:
Taco Finance is a decentralized yield farm on Binance Smart Chain  and PancakeSwap exchange.

A deflationary governance token model with a unique burn mechanism to stabilize TACO's price when there is a massive dump, rewarding and profitable yield with high APR. Besides, we have also implemented a timelock of 48 hours upon any contract changes, so that you can sleep peacefully while staking with us.
